import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Wildlife_Species'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wildlife species involved in bird strikes?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Aircraft_Make_Model'].value_counts().plot(kind='bar')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of aircraft make and model involved in bird strikes?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'].value_counts().plot(kind='pie', autopct='%1.1f%%')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of effect amount of damage caused by bird strikes?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Cost_Repair'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Cost_Repair'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['Cost_Repair'])
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.hist(data['Cost_Repair'], bins=50, color='blue', alpha=0.7)
    ax.axvline(data['Cost_Repair'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Cost_Repair'].median()))
    ax.legend(loc='best')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of cost of repair due to bird strikes?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Speed_IAS_in_knots'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Speed_IAS_in_knots'], errors='coerce')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.boxplot(data['Speed_IAS_in_knots'].dropna(), vert=False)
    ax.set_xlabel('Speed in Knots')
    ax.axvline(data['Speed_IAS_in_knots'].median(), color='r', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Speed_IAS_in_knots'].median()))
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of speed in knots during bird strikes?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
